node.text: Hello - noticed your page whilst exploring, @mrs_serene_lim - feel free to check out my page

Happy Labour Day!

Sharing some new food I tried!

Portobello stuffed w capsicum, tomato topped with cheese. I always like to eat mushroom this way. I tried cooking with air fryer previously and never really succeed (so simple dish also can fail, right?) Anyway I think I was too tired and I cooked the mushrooms without the cheese! Only realised after it’s done.. Then I saw the milo cake from @j3raine story and went to @vannytelly acct to check it out. I didn’t have 3-in-1 milo and condensed milk. So I made it with 81g of milo powder and one egg and steamed for 20 mins! It’s so thin because I used too big a plate.. 🤣🤣 Warning: it’s super heaty.

How has your #circuitbreakersg  days been so far? Jack will be returning to office next week and we will have another round of adjustments to make. For now, let me enjoy the holidayyyyyyyy
